\begin_layout Standard
The analysis focuses on the three main outcomes described in detailed Section 3.
 Gender gaps in maize productivity,
 gross income from maize and adoption of hybrid seeds varieties are first estimated using Ordinary Least Squares (OLS) regressions.
 The baseline specification is based on a standarrd agricultural production specification (Udry,
 1996) in the form:
 
